title: OBJ to Rams, Cam back to Panthers and Week 10 Preview
itunes:title: OBJ to Rams, Cam back to Panthers and Week 10 Preview
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal break down the latest news in the NFL including Odell Beckham Jr. to the Los Angeles Rams and Cam Newton is going back to Carolina! We also preview each of the upcoming Week 10 games and make our lock picks.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
